":538},{"title":"Author/Ramamoorthy Siva","target":"Author/Ramamoorthy Siva","line":539},{"title":"Author/Wasan Sriprom","target":"Author/Wasan Sriprom","line":540},{"title":"Author/Wasan Sriprom","target":"Author/Wasan Sriprom","line":541},{"title":"Author/T. S. Suryanarayanan","target":"Author/T. S. Suryanarayanan","line":542},{"title":"Author/Trichur S. Suryanarayanan","target":"Author/Trichur S. Suryanarayanan","line":543},{"title":"Author/Kanaporn Sujarit","target":"Author/Kanaporn Sujarit","line":544},{"title":"Author/Kanaporn Sujarit","target":"Author/Kanaporn Sujarit","line":545},{"title":"Author/Nakarin Suwannarach","target":"Author/Nakarin Suwannarach","line":546},{"title":"Author/Nakarin Suwannarach","target":"Author/Nakarin Suwannarach","line":547},{"title":"Author/Khamphe Phoungthong","target":"Author/Khamphe Phoungthong","line":548},{"title":"Author/Thitipone Suwunwong","target":"Author/Thitipone Suwunwong","line":549},{"title":"Author/Thitipone Suwunwong","target":"Author/Thitipone Suwunwong","line":550},{"title":"Author/Thitipone Suwunwong","target":"Author/Thitipone Suwunwong","line":551},{"title":"Author/Benjarong Thongbai","target":"Author/Benjarong Thongbai","line":552},{"title":"Author/Benjarong Thongbai","target":"Author/Benjarong Thongbai","line":553},{"title":"Author/Naritsada Thongklang","target":"Author/Naritsada Thongklang","line":554},{"title":"Author/Naritsada Thongklang","target":"Author/Naritsada Thongklang","line":555},{"title":"Author/De-Ping Wei","target":"Author/De-Ping Wei","line":556},{"title":"Author/Deping Wei","target":"Author/Deping Wei","line":557},{"title":"Author/Subodini N. Wijesinghe","target":"Author/Subodini N. Wijesinghe","line":558},{"title":"Author/S. Nuwanthika Wijesinghe","target":"Author/S. Nuwanthika Wijesinghe","line":559},{"title":"Author/Jake Winiski","target":"Author/Jake Winiski","line":560},{"title":"Author/Jake Winiski","target":"Author/Jake Winiski","line":561},{"title":"Author/Jiye Yan","target":"Author/Jiye Yan","line":562},{"title":"Author/Jiye Yan","target":"Author/Jiye Yan","line":563},{"title":"Author/Erandi Yasanthika","target":"Author/Erandi Yasanthika","line":564},{"title":"Author/Erandi Yasanthika","target":"Author/Erandi Yasanthika","line":565},{"title":"Author/Erandi Yasanthika","target":"Author/Erandi Yasanthika","line":566},{"title":"Author/Marc Stadler","target":"Author/Marc Stadler","line":567},{"title":"Author/Marc Stadler","target":"Author/Marc Stadler","line":568},{"title":"PDF","target":"biblib/hyde_amazing_2019/hyde_amazing_2019.pdf","line":570}],"metadata":{"id":"hyde_amazing_2019","type":"article-journal","title":"The amazing potential of fungi: 50 ways we can exploit fungi industrially","issued":{"date-parts":[[2019]]},"DOI":"10.1007/s13225-019-00430-9","container-title":"Fungal Diversity","abstract":"Fungi are an understudied, biotechnologically valuable group of organisms. Due to the immense range of habitats that fungi inhabit, and the consequent need to compete against a diverse array of other fungi, bacteria, and animals, fungi have developed numerous survival mechanisms. The unique attributes of fungi thus herald great promise for their application in biotechnology and industry. Moreover, fungi can be grown with relative ease, making production at scale viable. The search for fungal biodiversity, and the construction of a living fungi collection, both have incredible economic potential in locating organisms with novel industrial uses that will lead to novel products. This manuscript reviews fifty ways in which fungi can potentially be utilized as biotechnology. We provide notes and examples for each potential exploitation and give examples from our own work and the work of other notable researchers. We also provide a flow chart that can be used to convince funding bodies of the importance of fungi for biotechnological research and as potential products. Fungi have provided the world with penicillin, lovastatin, and other globally significant medicines, and they remain an untapped resource with enormous industrial potential.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Hyde","given":"Kevin D.","literal":""},{"family":"Hyde","given":"Kevin D.","literal":""},{"family":"Xu","given":"Jianchu","literal":""},{"family":"Xu","given":"Jianchu","literal":""},{"family":"Rapior","given":"Sylvie","literal":""},{"family":"Rapior","given":"Sylvie","literal":""},{"family":"Jeewon","given":"Rajesh","literal":""},{"family":"Jeewon","given":"Rajesh","literal":""},{"family":"Lumyong","given":"Saisamorn","literal":""},{"family":"Lumyong","given":"Saisamorn","literal":""},{"family":"Niego","given":"Allen Grace T.","literal":""},{"family":"Niego","given":"Allen Grace T.","literal":""},{"family":"Niego","given":"Allen Grace T.","literal":""},{"family":"Abeywickrama","given":"Pranami D.","literal":""},{"family":"Abeywickrama","given":"Pranami D.","literal":""},{"family":"Aluthmuhandiram","given":"Janith V. S.","literal":""},{"family":"Aluthmuhandiram","given":"Janith V. S.","literal":""},{"family":"Brahamanage","given":"Rashika S.","literal":""},{"family":"Brahamanage","given":"Rashika S.","literal":""},{"family":"Brooks","given":"Siraprapa","literal":""},{"family":"Brooks","given":"Siraprapa","literal":""},{"family":"Chaiyasen","given":"Amornrat","literal":""},{"family":"Chaiyasen","given":"Amornrat","literal":""},{"family":"Chethana","given":"K. W. Thilini","literal":""},{"family":"Chethana","given":"K. W. Thilini","literal":""},{"family":"Chomnunti","given":"Putarak","literal":""},{"family":"Chomnunti","given":"Putarak","literal":""},{"family":"Chepkirui","given":"Clara","literal":""},{"family":"Chepkirui","given":"Clara","literal":""},{"family":"Chuankid","given":"Boontiya","literal":""},{"family":"Chuankid","given":"Boontiya","literal":""},{"family":"Silva","given":"Nimali I. de","literal":""},{"family":"Silva","given":"Nimali I. de","literal":""},{"family":"Doilom","given":"Mingkwan","literal":""},{"family":"Do